Class Batiment

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Card
      • model.Batiment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Batiment
extends Card
    This class inherits the Card class. This class' objects represents different types of building that need resources to be finished. When a building is finished, it gives the player a certain amount of victory points.
